{"tid":1505250,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵總部明天26/8關閉","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T13:29:11.000Z","uid":72321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a595ee148ee4261735ee6475045d667462d26f","tid":1505250,"uid":72321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:22:08.000Z","msg":"企業保安部訊息<br />\n<br />\n保安公告：2019-08-26（星期一）關閉港鐵總部大樓<br />\n<br />\n一項可能進行的公眾活動，會對在港鐵總部大樓辦公的人員構成風險，故大樓將於2019年8月26日（星期一）關閉一天 。<br />\n<br />\n現通知各人員在8月26日（星期一）不要返回總部大樓。<br />\n<br />\n如需協助，請致電2993總部大樓控制中心，聯絡企業保安部人員。<br />\n<br />\n各部門主管須啟動業務持續計劃，作出相應業務安排，並儘早通知各受影響單位及人士。<br />\n<br />\n各部門代表:<br />\n<br />\n請適時通知各部門同事有關上述訊息。"},{"pid":"c7ad5983bb4db4d62e870766dfa1696e0c784678","tid":1505250,"uid":72321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"黨鐵怕了"},{"pid":"57cf62e72e08df340b2de963f0ffe6ece17b9462","tid":1505250,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"},{"pid":"648024842189ed0749a8eaebc4668c0fc8607101","tid":1505250,"uid":72321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:26:17.000Z","msg":"各位同事放假去機場玩玩啦"},{"pid":"2f5a230ad7b89f549649de73a93d80ea3db19ad8","tid":1505250,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:26:28.000Z","msg":"驚到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n借位推，大家入黎討論下！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>其實我地可唔可以自己開返個reddit咁既平台</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1504694/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1504694/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a497da994331a63eb7daec90d7d1a4e548417c71","tid":1505250,"uid":275524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:26:47.000Z","msg":"文宣請入：快d spin 呢條片 如果唔係中間派遲早比統戰 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1505177/page/1\" data-